overview:
We are an ISO 9001:2000 certified company engaged in manufacturing and supply of generation biological fertilizers, micronutrient fertilizers, plant fungicides, PGRs and bio pesticides. These are appreciated for their eco-friendliness.

Based in Nashik (Maharashtra), we have done exceedingly well in the sphere of manufacturing and supplying Micronutrient Fertilizers, Organic Fertilizers, Plant Growth Regulators, Humic Acid 12%, Spray Adjuvant, Fungicides and Biopesticides. These are used for various applications like pest control, seed treatment, root dipping, fertility restoration and soil nutrient management. We provide complete nutritional support to the plants.

We ensure that these fungicides, fertilizers and bio pesticides are manufactured as per the industrial standards. These are also tested for quality before being supplied to our clients who are based in every nook and corner of the country. We are the pioneer to introduce Amino Acid Based Micronutrient Fertilizer mixtures in INDIA with the brand name “EXCEED”. The product “Exceed” is very much popular among the farming comunity across the country. It is used almost in all cereals, pulses, vegetables, fruit crops, spices, oil seeds, floriculture etc.
